      • compareInodes

        public static final int compareInodes(java.lang.String inodeStr1,
                java.lang.String inodeStr2)
        Compares two inodes for ordering.
        Parameters:
        inodeStr1 - Inode.inode which is a String.
        inodeStr2 - Inode.inode which is a String.
        Returns:
        the value 0 if the Inode corresponding to inodeStr1 is created at the same time as Inode corresponding to inodeStr2. a value less than 0 if the Inode corresponding to inodeStr1 is created before the Inode corresponding to inodeStr2. and a value greater than 0 if the Inode corresponding to inodeStr1 is created after the Inode corresponding to inodeStr2.
